    v1 = 0.0

    v2 = 0.41
    v1 = tmp
    v2 = (0.44 * (wp.abs(v0 + 0.70) * tmp))
    v2 = wp.exp(v2)
    v2 = (0.37 - ((v2 + 0.29 / v1 + 0.02) * v2))
    v1 = 0.35
    v2 = 0.21
    v0 = (((v0 + 0.29 - v2 + 0.42) * (v0 + 0.52 + v2 + 0.59)) * (wp.exp(tmp + 0.91) / 0.60))
